subject: Print complex datatypes(hash table, Vectors)
msgSnippet: Hi, Whenever assert* or and JUnit test call fails or behaves unexpectedly, We need to dump the input/output, so that user can see why it failed or What
messageBody:
Hi,

Whenever assert* or and JUnit test call fails or
behaves unexpectedly, We need to dump the
input/output, so that user can see why it failed or
What happened? In case of complex data types like
Vector or Hash Table, we need to device a way to dump
it as well.This should happen whether we run it from
command line or from IDE like Eclipse. Can you please
help us to find the solution to print the values.
Thanks & Regards,
Bala
